Holdout		KEY:Trait ~ Holdout						SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Holdout]				DESC:You were robbed at a young age by bullies, an experience that impressed upon you the importance of being able to hold on to whatever you cared to keep. You gain a +1 trait bonus to CMD against disarm and steal combat maneuvers.
Inspiring		KEY:Trait ~ Inspiring						SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Inspiring]				DESC:As a child, you learned the power of a simple expression of fith in another when you gave a hero the inspiration to fght on in the face of terrible odds and save you fom danger. As a standard action, you can speak words of encouragement to grant a +1 morale bonus to an ally within 30 fe et who can see and hear you. The ally can use this bonus on any d2o roll of her choice befre the start of your next turn. You cannot use this trait to grant a bonus to yourself or to an ally who has already benefited fom this trait within the last 24 hours.
Pillager		KEY:Trait ~ Pillager						SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Pillager]				DESC:Growing up in a place where authorities, if there were any, rarely enfrced property laws, you learned quickly that you have only what you can hold-but you gain whatever you can take. You gain a +1 trait bonus on combat maneuver checks to perfrm disarm and steal combat maneuvers.
Soaring Sprinter	KEY:Trait ~ Soaring Sprinter					SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Soaring Sprinter]				DESC:As a youth, you often leaped and ran at treacherous heights, either because it was the only place with enough feedom for you to play or because it was not a good idea to play any lower. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Acrobatics checks to keep your balance or jump, and Acrobatics becomes a class skill for you.
Sworn Enemy		KEY:Trait ~ Sworn Enemy						SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Sworn Enemy]				DESC:You were raised with defance, fear, or hatred of a particular sort of fe. To make you ready to resist such fes, you were trained for long hours in the proper ways to defeat them. Choose a fe from the ranger's list of favored enemies. You gain a +1 trait bonus on attacks of opportunity against the chosen fe.
Vengeful		KEY:Trait ~ Vengeful						SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Vengeful]				DESC:During your childhood, you sufered occasional or fequent abuse fom those too powerfl for you to resist. Now you thrill at the chance to get back at those who wronged you. Whenever you strike the last creature that damaged you in the past 24 hours, you gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls against that creature.

