Authoritarian	KEY:Trait ~ Authoritarian					SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Authoritarian]				DESC:You spent much of your youth helping the clergy of your chosen fith perfrm their duties, and learned fom them respect for authority. As long as you are acting in the service of a liege or leader you recognize as legitimate, you gain a +2 trait bonus on saving throws against far and compulsion efects.
Called		KEY:Trait ~ Called						SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Called]				DESC:Your deity or a powerfl spirit spoke to you when you were young, dropping cryptic hints about the important destiny that lay befre you and how you must win your fghts if you are to achieve your predetermined greatness. Once per day upon rolling a natural 1 on an attack roll, you may reroll the die and take the second result instead.
Devoted Healer	KEY:Trait ~ Devoted Healer					SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Devoted Healer]				DESC:Raised in the company of skilled healers, you were always encouraged to devote your time and energy to the welfre of others. Whenever you take 20 on a Heal check to treat deadly wounds, you restore an additional id4 hit points to those you aid.
Honest		KEY:Trait ~ Honest						SOURCEPAGE:p.18	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Honest]				DESC:A religious mentor instilled in you a sense of uncompromising integrity. You ofen speak your mind in defance of any fear or hatred it might earn you, a habit that inspires others to trust you. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Diplomacy checks. This bonus increases to +2 when the Diplomacy check is made to influence those who are already fiendly or helpfl toward you.
Irrepressible	KEY:Trait ~ Irrepressible					SOURCEPAGE:p.19	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Irrepressible]				DESC:Your hope for a brighter future blessed by the gods, combined with your powerfl personality, allows you to frce your way fee of spells that cloud the mind. You can use your Charisma modifer in place of your Wisdom modifer when attempting Will saving throws against charm and compulsion efects.
Mystery Initiate	KEY:Trait ~ Mystery Initiate					SOURCEPAGE:p.19	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Mystery Initiate]				DESC:You were initiated into a mystery cult in your youth, and learned secrets that turned your understanding of your fith and the world on its head. This experience has given you a knack for lateral thinking. Once per day, you may reroll any Knowledge skill check. You must decide to use this ability after the frst roll is made but befre the results are revealed. You must take the second result, even ifit is worse.
Patient Calm	KEY:Trait ~ Patient Calm					SOURCEPAGE:p.19	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Patient Calm]				DESC:As a child, you struggled to suppress a community leader rubbed of on you. As you grew older, you developed a remarkable ability to keep calm and collected when perfrming a task you are fmiliar with. Choose one Craft or Profession skill. Whenever you take 10 with that skill, determine the result as if you had rolled a 12 instead ofa 10.
Spell Intuition	KEY:Trait ~ Spell Intuition					SOURCEPAGE:p.19	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.FaithTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.FaithTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Spell Intuition]				DESC:Blessed by a priest of a deity of magic at birth, you demonstrated a remarkable knack for guessing the nature of spells without the schooling of your instructors. You gain a +1 trait bonus on Spellcraft checks, and Spellcraft becomes a class skill for you.

