Anxious			KEY:Drawback ~ Anxious						COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.22	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Drawback	PREMULT:1,[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.Drawback],[PREVAREQ:BypassDrawbackRestriction,1],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Drawback ~ Anxious]				DESC:After sufering terribly for not being tight­lipped enough as a child, such as when you accidentally exposed your family to enemy inquisitors, you developed a habit of being overly cautious with your words. You take a -2 penalty on Diplomacy checks and must speak slowly due to the concentration required. Unless stated otherwise, you are assumed to not be speaking at a volume above a whisper.
